arStrings.szText:
Cantor Adiya,
Stop writing to me about the cave-ins and do as I told you previously! Dispose of the bodies in the tunnels. Give the families some coin to temper their anger.
Annoyed - a superior talking down to an underling who has disappointed him.

We need only a bit more stone to complete Omathâ€™s Stronghold, and your squeamishness will not jeopardize that. If you see this through, you can leave the mine to the locals and return to civilization. Or must I find another cantor who has the stomach for it?

Akarat give you strength,
Heirophant Harsa
